        "denominator": "Total Category Sales (All Brands – All Manufacturers – All Segments)",
        "formula": "Weighted Distribution (%) = (Brand Sales in Stores Selling Brand ÷ Total Category Sales) × 100",
        "explanation": """
Weighted Distribution measures the sales-weighted reach of a product.
It shows how important the stores are where the product is listed.
Unlike Numeric Distribution, it accounts for store sales size.
"""
